The hallway connected to the secret dance 
floor changed into a red Chinese-style design. 
Word on the street was that nobody got in
without the say-so of a regular.
[wait][clear][end]

msg_1:
It looked like the rumors that the Taiwanese 
mafia bought out this club were somehow true.
[wait][clear][end]

msg_2:
Before, when I came to do guidance for the 
students of Kasugayama High, Club Zodiac 
was a cheap place arranged with constellations, 
as the name implies.
[wait][clear][end]

msg_3:
While walking through a vulgar red corridor, 
the sort only the nouveau riche could like, 
I pulled out my cell and called a familiar number. 
[wait][clear]After the fifth ring, someone picked up the line. 
Just like before, the rumor was true.
[sync][wait][clear][end]

msg_4:
