[tab]You remember how I asked you to kill 
[tab]Shiori Miyashiro? She’s on the VIP floor 
[tab]at Club Zodiac in Yumezaki Ward.
[sync][wait][clear][end]

msg_5:
That’s all I said before I hung up the phone. 
There was no going back anymore. By the end
of the night, I’d know if the rumors were true or not. 
If I failed, I’d just add another corpse to the pile.
[sync][wait][clear][end]

